    "game-id": "0981d050ec66a7e8db88a30e00d89fd1",
    "spell_type": "spell",
    "rank": 4,
    "text": "A swirling torrent of water manifests along a straight line, battering creatures and unattended objects in its path and possibly pushing them away from you. The torrent deals 8d6 bludgeoning damage. Each creature in the area must attempt a basic Fortitude save; unattended objects automatically fail. Creatures and objects that fail are also knocked back 5 feet (10 feet on a critical failure).",
